<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><?ish ishref="GUID-7E80BD27-7678-408F-9B32-C9D1557A4DA0" version="1" lang="en-US"?><concept xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="GUID-7E80BD27-7678-408F-9B32-C9D1557A4DA0" xml:lang="en-US" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3" domains="(topic concept)                            (topic hi-d)                            (topic ui-d)                            (topic sw-d)                            (topic indexing-d)                            (topic ut-d)                            a(base ishcondition)                            a(base varid)                            a(base varref)                            a(base cid)                            a(base partslist)                            (topic oce-d)                            (topic sdlVariables-c)                            (topic oceCommonElements-c)                            (topic oceMetaDecl-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c concept oceConcept-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c hi-d oceHighlight-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c ui-d oceUi-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c sw-d oceSoftware-c)   " class="- topic/topic concept/concept "><title class="- topic/title ">15 The function of the X Motion System</title><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Functional description</category></metadata></prolog><conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody "><section id="GUID-F5034822-753A-4C8B-A7CD-E44CE7EBD702" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "><ph class="- topic/ph ">Definition</ph></title><p class="- topic/p ">The function of the X Motion System is split up in different functional sections as described below. 
</p><table id="GUID-44CC9D37-524C-4240-A579-9C6FC3D85313" pgwide="1" class="- topic/table "><tgroup cols="2" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="20*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="80*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Function 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Description 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">The Buffer 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><ol id="OL_4D5446901EDB431F97F08D9F6ACBC56D" class="- topic/ol "><li id="LI_66EA55D1134C473FAC174905C1C1702E" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Support the media from the input unit to the X Motion system. 
</p></li><li id="LI_3342C8283F614F1CBDEE47BA5E26284D" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Compensate steering and speed differences between the media drawer and the X Motion system. 
</p></li><li id="LI_9ABC21030C3C4029984C1D071D4446B4" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Heat the media to a certain temperature before it enters the X Motion system to prevent wrinkling on the print surface. 
</p></li><li id="LI_97B9E8EEAA7446FAAE5A0074CF592044" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove static charges after the buffer. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Detection of media blocking in the drawer. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Detection of roll empty ( blocking or not blocking the media path). 
</p></li></ol></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">The Xtran unit 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">The Xtran unit drives the media while it is on the platen. 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">The platen 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">The platen (print surface) performs the following functions : 
</p><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Support the media during transport 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Keep the media flat on the print/cure surface 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Keep the media on a controlled temperature 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Keep the media stable during cut 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Create contrast for the side edge detection and prevent reflection of the UV light 
</p></li></ol></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">The Xtran pinch lifter 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Open and close the Xtran pinch. 
</p></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-3225DD38-160F-42B4-A279-10AA00359615" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">For more extensive information see :</title><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="15FUNC02" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-32697AF0-BC89-480B-812D-46AF0F253E61.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="concept"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 15 The function of the buffer?>15 The function of the buffer</xref> 
</p><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="15FUNC03" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-7AEE1ECC-C765-4F0F-8B5A-D9E3E00A767B.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="concept"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 15 The drive of the Xtran unit?>15 The drive of the Xtran unit</xref> 
</p><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="15FUNC04" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-6D282AE7-7B2C-4535-A670-B929DB7DF0D1.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="concept"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 15 The function of the platen (print surface)?>15 The function of the platen (print surface)</xref> 
</p><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="15FUNC05" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-BC02304B-49F0-42B5-9ADB-0F9891FE5E3F.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="concept"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 15 The function of the Xtran pinch lifter?>15 The function of the Xtran pinch lifter</xref> 
